00:11:51.700 --> 00:11:53.410
So another shout out to the fact

00:11:53.410 --> 00:11:56.700
that the Library's collections
come in a huge variety of media,

00:11:56.700 --> 00:11:58.820
from motion picture
films to newspapers

00:11:58.820 --> 00:12:00.960
and periodicals to manuscripts.

00:12:00.960 --> 00:12:04.820
Library collections are so much
