There are about 3000 books
in the Library's collection

00:12:22.920 --> 00:12:25.920
that are either written by
Mark Twain or about Mark Twain.

00:12:25.920 --> 00:12:27.220
That's a lot.

00:12:27.220 --> 00:12:28.520
3000, that's incredible.

